Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一旦輪到她掃除就一定會逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紋次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人一定在行人身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到之後給你吃栗羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當古老的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要觸碰  很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身妖怪二尾狸貓幻十丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴密封印中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了啊  變身妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:19.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迷惑  pompoko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天完全沒收穫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的形勢發展下去  今天絕對不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的字典裡沒有絕對不可能這個詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  快點來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起吃來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來快來  看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微改變樂一下釣的地點  就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有絕對不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是魚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他顧不上吃點心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排  你剛才說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃紅豆大福  紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺有點增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  多多益善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚都變成樹葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險  差點被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  又是麻知的惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是幻十丸的花招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是狸貓妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調包東西或偽裝成人的樣子做壞事的討厭傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點重新封印它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸貓會偽裝成人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是童話故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完全都不信呢  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩隻炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定又是島虎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  那就是最好的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就算是偽裝了凸肚臍還是不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸貓妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是會魔術的狸貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在報復我這個封印它的巫女的子孫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強烈的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話村子裡也會出現受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都會幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  惡作劇有點過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喜歡變裝的狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要如何才能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算凸肚臍是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了衣服不就看不到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌貨總歸是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對話馬上就會露出馬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:07:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  幻十丸一旦暈過去變身就解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傢伙一出現就馬上用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是不偽裝就難受的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越多越容易偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出有什麼異樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  大家擺出很可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到奇怪的狸貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  鑽在茶壺裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶壺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩隻尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一副很會做惡作劇面孔的狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是像這種感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鰻魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有兩個我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回變成梅梅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是變  是化裝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  你們兩個能給我看一下肚臍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給我看肚臍的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個打到你們暈過去為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道梅梅的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能分出真假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的梅梅在鎖骨下面有兩顆痣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼行人會知道那裡有痣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛模仿的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關痣的事是我捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  被揭穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個黑色的球是對兩顆痣的回報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扮的很漂亮真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我也是女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這種不合身分的興趣對我來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被人知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  凜從沒穿過這種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著很女性化的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是凜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過分  連小鈴和公子都這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  真的是凜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著這種女性化的衣服是你的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著漂亮的和服去選簪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們居然這樣對待我私底下的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定又在變什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嫩豆腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連佐料都有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…可…饒…恕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影  有看到奇怪的狸貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是指鑽進茶壺裡的狸貓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才慌慌張張的進了井裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是井裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想耍我到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怨恨賭上巫女之名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剝了那偽裝的皮做成狸貓汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  那善於模仿的傢伙跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在烤秋刀魚變成草鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在煮大豆怎麼變成線球了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明放的是糖怎麼這麼鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真為難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話全村的人都值得懷疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能大意啊  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避掃除  在這玩什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了呢  幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一下沒暈倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這綾音不是凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去找下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然做什麼啊  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明被暴打了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一句認錯人了事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了姐姐大人你逃避掃除在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是掃除的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一些小事變身妖怪二尾狸貓幻十丸的封印被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這村子現在正處非常時期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那「小事」是指的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妖怪是我們的祖先大約在一百年前封印的品行糟糕的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算是個巫女  來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己掃除就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒說  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:02.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(啊～這到底是怎麼一回事啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  有兩個我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙  和在下一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺看起來很友好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情又不是才現在出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是在下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(什麼  你這冒牌貨)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你才是冒牌貨)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真分不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這樣的話就決鬥吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼果然只能讓雙方都暈倒一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為像那麼弱小的東西能贏過在下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他方陣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影之太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一樣的有八人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越分不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一瞬間將忍的腰帶全部解開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人數不這樣做的話是無法確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要一人解決兩個忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真身…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就讓它得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天一直都被那妖怪狸貓耍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦扯牽到姐姐大人就沒好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  明明那麼努力了還是抓不到那狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要在今天抓住它絕對不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也許不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  估計是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了  幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個行人就是狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來發洩怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也必須被綁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當然在意啦)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  居然能辨別出行人是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為這行人稱狸貓是妖怪狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的行人不相信妖怪和怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就故意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對不可能」這會讓行人一瞬間認真起來的詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  估計是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人不可能會是那種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一同生活的優勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐  你有說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才把綾音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻十丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為能從我手中逃脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想帶你參觀八天七夜地獄旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經落日了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈封印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣就封印了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次解除是在幾十年之後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  真正的行人大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  妖怪狸貓什麼的怎麼可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是死腦筋  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是啊  像這種只有在童話故事中出現的東西)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上說  是很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這行人大人是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  需要確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是明擺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認是否是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把全身剝得一乾二淨地檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,80)}{\fad(800,800)\fs20\bord3\4a&HFF}\N\N\N\N{\1c&HC43A2C\3c&HFFFFFF}次回　　　　　　　{\fs10}\N\N{\fs20}「想找到  藍鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經無路可走了  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把肚臍…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧  兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知  不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pompoko
